title: MS_MN_series_ISO.zip
description:
This is the Microsoft Broadband Networking Version 2.0 disk 

This has the files to install the MN-5090 and MN-700 base stations, and the following network adapter cards:
MN-110
MN-120
MN-130
MN-510
MN-520
MN-720
MN-730

My MN-730 installed without a problem on XP  SP2 Pro,
but I needed the original disk for XP SP2 Home.

I had to Add Hardware, and browse to the root directory
for theses drivers to get it installed, the setup etc did not
work for me.
